# Frontend mirror

Treat **`f1-web-server/frontend/`** as the primary web UI worktree.

After editing any file under that folder, mirror the same change to **`f1-web-local/web/public/`** using the same filename:

| Server (`f1-web-server/frontend/`) | Local (`f1-web-local/web/public/`) |
|-----------------------------------|-------------------------------------|
| `app.js`, `view3d.js`, `styles.css`, `index.html`, `config.js` | same names |

**Do not copy** server-only deploy assets into local: `package.json`, `vercel.json`, `scripts/` (Vercel build).

Shared static data under `data/` should stay consistent when it changes (schedule JSON, `default-year.json`).
